      "ruleId": "ifrs9-r002",
      "paragraphReference": "IFRS 9.B4.1.7",
      "ruleText": "Financial assets are measured at amortised cost only if held within a hold-to-collect business model and contractual terms give rise to cash flows that are solely payments of principal and interest (SPPI).",
