      "paragraphReference": "IFRS 9.5.5.1",
      "ruleText": "An entity shall recognise a loss allowance for expected credit losses on financial assets measured at amortised cost, at fair value through other comprehensive income (debt), and certain loan commitments and financial guarantee contracts.",
